//DISCLAIMER Change Language Disclaimer
The “WiScan” (We Scan) app is designed solely for the purpose of capturing local WiFi data (BSSIDs, SSIDs, security protocols, and corresponding location data), cleaning the data, displaying progress to the user, and sending the data for advanced visualizations such as graphs and maps. The app allows configuration through user controls like WiFi scan frequency and radius.\n\n Important Notice:\n\n - The WiScan app must be used exclusively for its intended purpose as described above.\n\n - Users are prohibited from using the app for any malicious activities, including but not limited to unauthorized access, interference with network security, or privacy violations.\n\n - By using the WiScan app, you agree to abide by all applicable laws and regulations regarding data collection and privacy.\n\n - The developers of WiScan are not responsible for any misuse of the app.
